;; This is a way to hook tempo into cc-mode. In fact, I merge here many ressources, including:
;; - http://www.lysator.liu.se/~davidk/elisp/tempo-examples.html
;; - http://svn.marc.abramowitz.info/homedir/dotfiles/emacs
